videos.headline: Georgia connects on pass for big gain
videos.description: Georgia QB Jake Fromm hooks up with Terry Godwin for a 28-yard pass and moves them to the Georgia 39-yard line.

videos.headline: Georgia hits big on jet sweep to open scoring
videos.description: Georgia WR Mecole Hardman gets the ball on a jet sweep and takes it 35 yards to the house giving Georgia a 7-0 lead.

videos.headline: Georgia interception gifts Mizzou ball in red zone
videos.description: Georgia QB Jake Fromm is intercepted by Cale Garret, giving Missouri the ball at Georgia's five-yard line.

videos.headline: Missouri shovel pass ties game
videos.description: Missouri QB Drew Lock hits Albert Okwuegbunam with a four-yard shovel pass for a touchdown to tie the game.

videos.headline: Georgia deep ball puts them in Missouri territory
videos.description: Georgia QB Jake Fromm connects with Javon Wims for a 30-yard gain to move to Missouri's 40-yard line.

videos.headline: Georgia's Ridley makes tough catch for go-ahead TD
videos.description: Georgia QB Jake Fromm hits Riley Ridley for a 19-yard touchdown pass.

videos.headline: Missouri answers with 63-yard TD pass to tie game
videos.description: Missouri QB Drew Lock connects with Emanuel Hall for a 63-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Georgia's Chubb hurdles defender
videos.description: Georgia RB Nick Chubb takes the handoff and hurdles a defender on his way to a 20-yard gain.

videos.headline: Michel's 36-yard dash puts Georgia on top
videos.description: Georgia RB Sony Michel takes the handoff 36-yards for the touchdown and gives them a 21-14 lead on Missouri.

videos.headline: Missouri's Hall catches second 63-yard TD
videos.description: Missouri QB Drew Lock hooks up with Emanuel Hall for his second 63-yard touchdown of the game.

videos.headline: Georgia hits pass for 50-yard gain as Woerner hurdles defender
videos.description: Georgia QB Jake Fromm hits Charlie Woerner who hurdles a defender on way to a big gain.

videos.headline: Georgia's 4-yard rush TD gives them breathing room
videos.description: Georgia QB Jake Fromm keeps it and dives into the end zone for a four-yard rushing touchdown.

videos.headline: UGA's Sanders grabs 14th career INT
videos.description: Missouri QB Drew Lock is picked off by Dominick Sanders who returns it to the Missouri 41-yard line.

videos.headline: Smart: 'Not playing good defense against explosive plays'
videos.description: Georgia head coach Kirby Smart breaks down how Missouri has kept in close and what he has seen from his quarterback Jake Fromm.

videos.headline: Georgia gets ball in red zone after Missouri botched punt
videos.description: Missouri punter Corey Fatony can't handle the bad snap and gets taken down for a loss of 18 yards, giving Georgia the ball at the Missouri 10-yard line.

videos.headline: Big run sets up Georgia TD
videos.description: Georgia RB D'Andre Swift takes the handoff 71 yards to the Missouri 11-yard line.

videos.headline: Georgia widens gap with rush TD
videos.description: Georgia RB Sony Michel gets handoff and runs 16 yards for a touchdown to build a 47-21 lead.

videos.headline: Missouri gets one back with 27-yard TD
videos.description: Missouri QB Drew Lock hooks up with Jason Reese for a 27-yard touchdown pass.

videos.headline: Missouri LB ejected for targeting during kick return
videos.description: Missouri LB Tavon Ross is ejected for targeting after his hit on Georgia's Mecole Hardman.

videos.headline: Georgia's Hardman turns on jets for 59-yard TD
videos.description: Georgia QB Jake Fromm hits Mecole Hardman for a 59-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Smart: 'Our offense was spectacular today'
videos.description: Coach Kirby Smart, RB Sony Michel and LB Roquan Smith break down Georgia's offensive explosion against Missouri and how the defense can get better.
